-- B y   K e v i n   C o s t e l l o e
-- 
2011-05-20T20:27:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/imf-approves-36-8-billion-portugal-loan-in-joint-rescue-package-with-eu.html
The International Monetary Fund said
today it approved a 26 billion-euro loan to  Portugal  as part of
a joint rescue package with the European Union.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
